State-owned Eskom has extended an invitation to interested parties to submit a tender for the provision of design, engineering, procurement, construction, construction management, start-up, commissioning, performance testing, and operator and maintenance training of a solar agrivoltaics or photovoltaic system for the Komati power station. The tender deadline is 10:00 on July 7 and a non-compulsory clarification meeting will be conducted virtually on Microsoft Teams on June 15. All interested tenderers are invited to submit their names and email addresses two days prior to the meeting to LebjanH@eskom.co.za. A site visit can also be requested by the tenderers and shall be arranged if necessary. More information is available at: www.sapvia.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Invitation-to-Tender-for-Komati-PV-Solar.pdf